ℹ️ About Us

The Galley on the River offers fresh cuisine, relaxed dining, and stunning river views right on the Bon Secour River. Whether you arrive by boat at our 70-foot pier or by car, we’re the perfect spot for any occasion.

We specialize in locally-sourced dishes and handcrafted drinks, from our famous seafood platters and Ahi Tuna Nachos to hand-pressed burgers and wood-fired pizzas. Every visit is a fresh experience.

Perfect For: Date night, family dinner, waterfront lunch, group celebrations, or just relaxing with a cold drink by the river.

✨ What Sets Us Apart
✅ Waterfront river views
✅ 70' boat-accessible pier
✅ Locally-sourced ingredients
✅ Handcrafted cocktails
✅ Hook & Cook service
✅ Outdoor riverside seating
✅ Fresh seafood daily
✅ Homemade desserts
